    <string name="general_information">Add the battery tile to your Quick Settings panel to check the battery level at a glance, or enable a persistent notification for detailed battery information and customizable alerts.\n\nThis app does not send any data outside your device and does not require internet access. It also requests no special permissions, so you can use it with confidence.</string>

    <string name="battery_charged_section_title">Battery charged notification</string>
    <string name="battery_charged_section_body">You can configure the level of charge required to consider the device charged, the delay for the first notification, and whether you want recurring notifications.\n\nPlease note that if you select a value lower than 100%, the device will continue to charge until you unplug it.</string>
